悬架损坏，空气弹簧滑出，车辆继续滑行，摆臂以及减振器等受到磨损。车辆检测结果为事故的外力受损，非产品质量问题。 小米回应“SU7被曝过坑时发生断轴”：不实，超速驾驶导致事故_澎湃质量观_澎湃新闻-The Paper"},"attached_info":"CkIIxO++zNy6kdpMEAMaCTExMzMxNjUzNiDWrKC9BjAAOP4DQANyCzExNzA0MTEyMzMweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"542 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f9e1484ed64b667bfbfa0f28c8071a9a_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1739117996.832526","card_id":"Q_828901579","target":{"id":828901579,"title":"如何看待Steam商店页面明确出现警告：数字版游戏只是租赁，不是购买？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/828901579","type":"question","created":1728707951,"answer_count":687,"follower_count":1506,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1314,16821,53547],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"据说和美国修正法律有关？"},"attached_info":"CkAIxO++zNy6kdpMEAMaCTExMTA5ODI4NyDv+qe4BjAAOOILQARyCTgyODkwMTU3OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"322 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a13fa96124fbe1eaa7938f2834fd0ed9_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1739117996.832821","card_id":"Q_10349019033","target":{"id":10349019033,"title":"欧洲本土人越来越少，外来移民越来越多，欧洲有被腾笼换鸟的危险，是不是说明欧洲文明并没有优越性？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/10349019033","type":"question","created":1737604735,"answer_count":90,"follower_count":234,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2918,50495,154716],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkIIxO++zNy6kdpMEAMaCTExMzA0NjAyNyD//Ma8BjAAOOoBQAVyCzEwMzQ5MDE5MDMzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"179 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-